{%- comment -%}
  CUSTOM (Hamamdoeken): rendert de artikel-content en vervangt product-shortcodes door een rij
  product-cards op exact die plek in de tekst.

  Gebruik in de blog-editor (op een eigen regel):
    [products:handle-1,handle-2,handle-3]
  De handles zijn de product-handles (het laatste deel van de product-URL /products/<handle>).

  Tekstdelen worden in losse .rte-wrappers gezet zodat de .rte-styling de product-cards niet raakt.

  Params:
    content  (string)  - de te renderen HTML (meestal article.content)
    columns  (int)     - aantal kolommen op desktop (default 3)
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign body_columns = columns | default: 3 -%}
{%- assign segments = content | split: '[products:' -%}
<div class="rte">{{ segments[0] }}</div>
{%- for segment in segments offset: 1 -%}
  {%- assign raw_handles = segment | split: ']' | first -%}
  {%- assign rest = segment | remove_first: raw_handles | remove_first: ']' -%}
  {%- assign handles = raw_handles | split: ',' -%}
  <div class="f-article-products f-grid f-grid-2-cols lg:f-grid-{{ body_columns }}-cols f-grid--gap-medium f-grid--row-gap-large">
    {%- for h in handles -%}
      {%- assign handle = h | strip -%}
      {%- assign card_product = all_products[handle] -%}
      {%- if card_product != blank and card_product != empty -%}
        {% render 'product-card', product: card_product, index: forloop.index %}
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
  <div class="rte">{{ rest }}</div>
{%- endfor -%}
